➜这家网红餐厅，被周杰伦告了！
http://www.sohu.com/a/413900833_767787	31171
<p class="ql-align-center">周杰伦的粉丝们应该都知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">福建厦门有一家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“网红店”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>↓↓↓</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/d2d22de237c440fba46deb91b055ac71.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图/网友：@温迪Wendy--</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">店里无论是装修、菜品、背景乐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满满都是“周董”相关的元素</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/231f79389229454f9aa26bbb5ef7584c.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">图/网友：@周杰伦讲笑话</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然而这家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">超多粉丝打卡的“网红店”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>被诉并未获得周杰伦的授权！</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
