<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>主动来到马场当义工</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>照顾第三匹“救命恩马”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200819/20d441d3b83a4b64951e0730f6c98945.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">姚大哥在福建晋江当地从事服装相关工作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>他说小时候也养过马</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>马非常聪明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>自己对马很有感情</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到“救命恩马”去世的消息感到非常可惜</p>
